    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on bumpy roads. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid, honest car for someone who needs dependable transportation and doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections and upcoming routine maintenance.",
